    "To avert the dissonance of scarcity and surplus, a global classification of crops during their seasonal crescendo becomes imperative [17].",
    "A view of land transformation unfolds, extending the frontiers of effective croplands by repurposing fallow expanses.",
    "Yet, this ballet is not without consequences-abrupt land conversion, a metaphorical thunderclap, amplifies greenhouse gas emissions, casting a shadow over climate and local ecosystems.",
